{"tid":2298692,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"酒吧界批政府隨便開刀「交功課」：跳舞群組的闊太不會去酒吧","createTime":"2020-11-24T08:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T16:34:10.000Z","uid":20933,"like":571,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":107,"replies":[{"pid":"cc1c29709d1b20585fc74d09758838c25013d13f","tid":2298692,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:30:15.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】消息指政府將會要求酒吧、卡拉OK及夜總會、浴室等暫停營業，宴會四人一枱，最多10枱。有酒吧業認為今次爆發與酒吧無關，無理由要酒吧停業。<br />\n<br />\n酒吧業協會副主席錢雋永：「現在是跳舞群組爆發，『闊太』不會去酒吧的，應該針對這班『闊太』去的地方，針對這些跳舞群組爆發的地方去關閉，而不是殃及池魚，走去關閉其他，不是引爆這個『炸彈』的地方。如果你說有酒吧群組爆發，你要我們關門，我們都會理解，但現在並非如此，你要酒吧和其他娛樂場所關閉，這是不能理解的，我們會覺得你是隨便找一些行業『開刀』，當是『交功課』。」"},{"pid":"4fdfd3e2a79d381b116f929ccf04b9cbbce8d057","tid":2298692,"uid":20933,"like":78,"dislike":3,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:30:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/40708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F40708&d=axquv7MewSEsfpkSD3%2FEaOdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=ed576e8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F40708&h=0cd3acfe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/40708</a>"},{"pid":"1a8544d04da089598c93197a1613bf472b751003","tid":2298692,"uid":28279,"like":398,"dislike":0,"score":398,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:31:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />政府點敢真係郁班有錢佬"},{"pid":"845be79f6bea6096e05beb3550e5b85f6434cda5","tid":2298692,"uid":341865,"like":427,"dislike":2,"score":425,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:31:14.000Z","msg":"好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />次次都係酒吧死先"},{"pid":"44391170bffa22bff8cda1921b060ed897c2d18e","tid":2298692,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img sr